INSERT INTO `plugin` VALUES ('plugin-a69ced94-e2ae-4151-a3f0-0f00cb76ed52', 'app.filtir.com', 'factcheck', 'https://app.filtir.com/.well-known/openapi.yml', 'factcheck', 'Filtir', 'Fact-check a given text. Given the text, it is your job to extract all the discrete factual claims or logical assertions. Each claim should be represented as a short concise sentence. Make sure that each sentence is very short and contains only one claim. Call the api one claim at a time. The api will return a list of evidences found for the claim. Your task is to assess whether a claim is correct based on the given pieces of evidence. Make sure that you read each piece of evidence found and asses if the claim is fully supported, partially supported or unsupported. For example, if the claim is â€œLondon is a city in Franceâ€ and the evidence is â€œLondon is a city in the UKâ€ then the claim is unsupported. If the claim is â€œLondon is a city in Franceâ€ and the evidence is â€œParis is a city in Franceâ€ then the claim is unsupported. Report back the decision for each claim along with a justification and with the references. If the link repeats for different claims, cite it only once.', 'Verify the provided text using external sources.', 'https://app.filtir.com/static/filtir-logo.png', 'contact@filtir.com', 'https://app.filtir.com/terms', 'å¯¹ç»™å®šçš„æ–‡æœ¬è¿›è¡Œäº‹å®æ£€æŸ¥ã€‚ç»™å‡ºæ–‡æœ¬åï¼Œæ‚¨çš„å·¥ä½œæ˜¯æå–æ‰€æœ‰ç‹¬ç«‹çš„äº‹å®é™ˆè¿°æˆ–é€»è¾‘æ–­è¨€ã€‚æ¯ä¸ªå£°æ˜éƒ½åº”è¡¨ç¤ºä¸ºç®€æ´çš„çŸ­å¥ã€‚ç¡®ä¿æ¯ä¸ªå¥å­éå¸¸ç®€çŸ­ï¼Œå¹¶ä¸”ä»…åŒ…å«ä¸€ä¸ªå£°æ˜ã€‚æ¯æ¬¡è°ƒç”¨ä¸€ä¸ªå£°æ˜çš„APIã€‚APIå°†è¿”å›æ‰¾åˆ°çš„è¯æ®åˆ—è¡¨ã€‚æ‚¨çš„ä»»åŠ¡æ˜¯æ ¹æ®ç»™å®šçš„è¯æ®è¯„ä¼°å£°æ˜æ˜¯å¦æ­£ç¡®ã€‚ç¡®ä¿æ‚¨é˜…è¯»æ¯ä¸ªæ‰¾åˆ°çš„è¯æ®ï¼Œå¹¶è¯„ä¼°å£°æ˜æ˜¯å¦å¾—åˆ°å…¨é¢æ”¯æŒã€éƒ¨åˆ†æ”¯æŒæˆ–ä¸æ”¯æŒã€‚ä¾‹å¦‚ï¼Œå¦‚æœå£°æ˜æ˜¯â€œä¼¦æ•¦æ˜¯æ³•å›½çš„åŸå¸‚â€ï¼Œè¯æ®æ˜¯â€œä¼¦æ•¦æ˜¯è‹±å›½çš„åŸå¸‚â€ï¼Œåˆ™è¯¥å£°æ˜ä¸è¢«æ”¯æŒã€‚å¦‚æœå£°æ˜æ˜¯â€œä¼¦æ•¦æ˜¯æ³•å›½çš„åŸå¸‚â€ï¼Œè¯æ®æ˜¯â€œå·´é»æ˜¯æ³•å›½çš„åŸå¸‚â€ï¼Œåˆ™è¯¥å£°æ˜ä¸è¢«æ”¯æŒã€‚å¯¹äºæ¯ä¸ªå£